      "COUNCIL WASHINGTON, D.C. 20506 March 28, 1989 ACTION MEMORANDUM FOR BRENT SCOWCROFT FROM: RICHARD N. HAASS RH SUBJECT: Middle East Peace Process Given our conversation of late yesterday, the upcoming NSC and next week's visits, I thought it important to get the attached memo up to you and over to the President. It is an attempt here to summarize as succinctly as I can just",
      "N THROUGH: RICHARD N. HAASS FROM: C. DAVID WELCH SUBJECT: Addition to Guest List for Dinner in Honor of Prime Minister Shamir We recommend you sign the attached memo to Melvyn Levitsky agreeing to invite the Ambassador of Egypt to the Shamir dinner. We suggest you discuss including the Israeli pool journalists with the White House Social office. RECOMMENDATION Th",
