      "PERSIAN GULF AND WORK ON A CEASEFIRE RESOLUTION BY THE UNSC, REGIONAL ARMS CONTROL AND EMBARGOES, AND PROSPECTS FOR THE MIDDLE EAST PEACE PROCESS. IN ADDITION TO MR. KIMMITT, IO AS BOLTON, ACTING EUR AS DOBBINS, S/P DEPUTY DIRECTOR BURNS, NSCS SENIOR DIRECTOR HAASS, AND EUR/RPE DIRECTOR KAUZLARICH {NOTETAKER} PARTICIPATED FOR THE U.S. THE EC SIDE WAS HEADED BY GOL POLITICAL",
