      "224 (Officer name) (Office symbol) (Extension) (Room number) MESSAGE DESCRIPTION CABLE TO MOSCOW: ACRS: READOUT OF U.S. MIDDLE EAST CONSULTATION TRIP AND AGENDA/SCHEDULE FOR UPCOMING MOSCOW MEETING TO: (Agency) DELIVER TO: Extension Room No. NSCS William- Sittmann 456-6534 WHSitrm NSCS Kenneth Hill 456-6534 WHSitrm NSCS Executive Secretariat 456-6534 WHSitrm Buens HAAS",
      "WED TO YOU LAST WEEK, A U.S. INTERAGENCY TEAM TRAVELED TO THE REGION DURING THE WEEK OF AUGUST 17 TO CONSULT JORDANIAN, ISRAELI, AND EGYPTIAN OFFICIALS ON PREPARATIONS FOR THE MOSCOW ACRS MEETING. AT EACH STOP, THE TEAM PRESENTED U.S. THINKING ALONG THE LINES CONVEYED TO YOU LAST WEEK AND SOLICITED REGIONAL PARTY REACTIONS. -- IN PARTICULAR, WHILE THE U.S. TEAM SUP",
