    "evidenceSnippets": [
      ". IN ADDITION, THE DEPARTMENT HAS DECIDED TO STOP ISSUING MULTIPLE DIPLOMATIC AND OFFICIAL PASSPORTS FOR THE PURPOSE OF MIDDLE EAST TRAVEL. -- THUS, YOU WILL BE SEEING MORE AND MORE DIPLOMATIC AND OFFICIAL PASSPORTS THAT REFLECT TRAVEL TO ISRAEL. IF YOU CURRENTLY RESTRICT ENTRY OR DENY VISAS TO PERSONS WHOSE TRAVEL DOCUMENTS REFLECT TRAVEL TO ISRAEL, WE URGE YOU TO CHA",
      "DIPLOMATIC AND OFFICIAL PASSPORTS FOR USE IN ARAB LEAGUE COUNTRIES AS A MATTER OF CUSTOMARY POLICY. AFTER APRIL 25, NO \"ISRAEL-ONLY\" PASSPORTS WILL BE VALID, AND SECOND DIPLOMATIC AND OFFICIAL PASSPORTS WILL BE ROUTINELY ISSUED ONLY TO CERTAIN DESIGNATED GROUPS SUCH AS TECHNICAL PERSONNEL WITH REGION-WIDE RESPONSIBILITIES WHO MAY NEED TO TRAVEL ON AN EMERGENCY BAS",
      "SEFUL PURPOSE. MANY AMERICANS SEE IT AS AN EFFORT TO INTERFERE WITH THEIR FREEDOM OF TRAVEL. -- IT DOES NOT ADVANCE THE PALESTINIAN CAUSE IN ANY CONCRETE MANNER, AND IT IS INCONSISTENT WITH THE ARAB WORLD'S STATED INTEREST IN MOVING TOWARD A PEACEFUL SETTLEMENT WITH ISRAEL. WE URGE YOU TO CHANGE THOSE POLICIES WHICH PREVENT YOUR ISSUING VISAS OR ALLOWING ENTRY TO PERSO"
    ],
