      "56: N/A TAGS: OPDC; JO SUBJECT: BIRTHDAY MESSAGE FROM THE PRESIDENT L. PLEASE DELIVER THE FOLLOWING BIRTHDAY MESSAGE TO KING HUSSEIN FROM PRESIDENT BUSH: BEGIN TEXT: YOUR MAJESTY: ON THE OCCASION OF YOUR BIRTHDAY, PLEASE ACCEPT PERSONAL BEST WISHES FROM BARBARA AND MYSELF AS WELL AS THOSE OF THE AMERICAN PEOPLE FOR YOUR AND YOUR FAMILY'S CONTINUED HEALTH AND HAPPINESS."
