      "tion will not allow Iraq to deflect attention from its illegal invasion of Kuwait by claiming there is a linkage to the Arab-Israeli conflict. The international community, including numerous Arab and Islamic nations, shares this view. The United States Government will continue to work diligently for the peaceful resolution of these two distinctly different but sensitive",
